    hybrid_encryption: Kyber768,
}
```

Key Features:

· 128-bit quantum security level using NIST-approved algorithms
· 2-second finality with 10,000+ TPS capability
· Hybrid classical/quantum-resistant cryptography for backward compatibility
· Energy-efficient proof-of-stake with carbon offset validation

