├── Non-Custodial Handling: Secure message retrieval
├── Privacy: Minimal data sharing with ZK proofs
└── Cross-Jurisdiction: Adaptive to local regulations
```

6.1.2 AML/CTF Engine

Real-time risk scoring with machine learning:

```python
class AMLCTFEngine:
    def assess_transaction(self, tx):
        risk_factors = {
            'sanctions': self.check_sanctions(tx.parties),
            'pattern': self.detect_suspicious_patterns(tx),
            'network': self.analyze_transaction_network(tx),
            'behavior': self.check_behavioral_anomalies(tx.user),
            'geographic': self.assess_jurisdiction_risk(tx),
        }
        
        risk_score = self.calculate_risk_score(risk_factors)
        
        return RiskAssessment(
            score=risk_score,
            action=self.determine_action(risk_score),
            required_verification=self.get_verification_requirements(risk_score)
        )
```

