7.2 Monetary Policy

7.2.1 Dynamic Supply Adjustment

```
Supply Adjustment = f(Price Deviation, Reserve Ratio, Economic Activity)

Where:
- Price Deviation: Difference from target CPI basket
- Reserve Ratio: Current backing vs required backing
- Economic Activity: Transaction volume, velocity
```

7.2.2 Interest Rate Framework

```
Base Rate = α × Inflation + β × Growth + γ × Environmental Impact + δ × Security

Components:
- Inflation (40%): Maintain price stability
- Growth (30%): Support economic activity
- Environmental (20%): Reward green transactions
- Security (10%): Ensure network integrity
```

